Target Users

Primary Users

Project Managers responsible for planning, tracking, and delivering projects.
PMO teams that oversee multiple projects and monitor organizational performance.
Scrum Masters and Product Managers coordinating Agile teams.
Cross-functional teams including developers, QA engineers, designers, and business analysts who collaborate on project execution.

Secondary Users

Senior leadership and department heads who require project dashboards and progress reports.
Clients and external stakeholders who need visibility into project milestones and deliverables.

Decision Makers

PMO Directors, CTOs, CIOs, and Operations Leaders responsible for selecting and implementing enterprise project management solution
